{"tid":1135240,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返咗一個星期就想辭職","createTime":"2019-05-02T07:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T16:44:46.000Z","uid":147699,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5eef524c55156c2a3fdd84697559fa860a8d0f61","tid":1135240,"uid":147699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:40:52.000Z","msg":"其實係我朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢幾日開解咗佢好耐<br />\n佢都係話好難上手 好多嘢記 做唔嚟等等<br />\n因為我自己都係返sales <br />\n一開始都覺得好吃力<br />\n但返耐咗就上咗手 <br />\n萬事起頭難 我都係咁去鼓勵佢<br />\n但佢一返工 又話唔想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我再逼佢做落去係好事定害佢？<br />\n定支持佢返多一個月再睇下點？<br />\n呢一兩年佢已經轉咗幾份工 再轉我唔知佢可以做邊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fdd49a019e8cb86940b4aa3f27a94f8e357700","tid":1135240,"uid":109655,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:42:56.000Z","msg":"sales唔係人人做得黎 做唔掂就趁早走唔好浪費時間"},{"pid":"c898dbe9f7a33396ec79bda8d867cfd1764b057e","tid":1135240,"uid":147699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85fdd49a019e8cb86940b4aa3f27a94f8e357700","tid":1135240,"uid":109655,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:42:56.000Z","msg":"sales唔係人人做得黎 做唔掂就趁早走唔好浪費時間"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:45:16.000Z","msg":"唔做sales 冇學歷可以揾咩工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0cf0ff72430d17daeeec0b81cc7bdb2c6ff4ef","tid":1135240,"uid":236335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:46:42.000Z","msg":"咪鬼理佢啦樓主<br />\n聽完安慰完咪算囉<br />\n佢咁大個人 你俾完意見佢佢都未必聽㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9afcbf785b023c9264312ff6f0fef721cdf5ebde","tid":1135240,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c898dbe9f7a33396ec79bda8d867cfd1764b057e","tid":1135240,"uid":147699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85fdd49a019e8cb86940b4aa3f27a94f8e357700","tid":113524